## Quick tables

### Radius

| Class | Use |
| --- | --- |
| `rounded-4xl` | Button, Badge, filter pills |
| `rounded-lg` | Input, Select, Textarea, Toggle, Alert |
| `rounded-xl` | Card, Dialog, Sheet, Empty/NoData |
| `rounded-2xl` | `Container`, nested tiles |
| `rounded-3xl` | Escrow panels / grid cards |
| `rounded-full` | Avatar, Switch, status dots |
| `rounded-md` | Menu items, Skeleton, tab triggers — **not** buttons |

### Colors (product)

Semantic only: `bg-background`, `bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`, `bg-primary` (`#006be4`), `text-destructive`, `bg-muted`. Soft destructive: `bg-destructive/10`. Edge: `ring-1 ring-foreground/10`.

**Forbidden in features:** `bg-blue-*`, `text-green-600`, `emerald-*`, `purple-*`, arbitrary hex (except ambient `Lights`).

### Density

| Control | Size |
| --- | --- |
| Input / Select / Toggle | `h-8` |
| Button | `h-9` · `sm` → `h-8` · header CTAs → `size="sm"` |
| Badge | `h-5` `text-xs` |
| Icons | `size-4` · compact `3`/`3.5` · header `5`→`6` |
| Gaps | controls `gap-1.5` · sections `gap-4`/`gap-6` · FieldGroup `gap-5` |

Prefer **`gap-*`** over `space-x`/`space-y` (ok `space-y` for title→description only).

### Badge status

disputed → `destructive` · released/resolved → `secondary` · flags `outline`/`default` · active → inverted + `LiveStatusDot` (named exception). Do not use Badge `success` for domain status.

