## House recipes (one-liners)

```tsx
// Page header title
"text-pretty text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-3xl"
// Section title
"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight"
// Container
"w-full rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card/40 p-6 shadow-sm"
// Escrow detail panel
"rounded-3xl border border-border bg-card p-6 sm:p-8"
// Filter bar
"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-3 md:p-4"
// Dual list
"md:hidden" cards + "hidden md:block" table
// Dialog footer
Cancel variant="outline" → primary action right
// Empty
<NoData title="…" />
```

Shell pad: `p-4 md:px-8`. Navbar: `h-14 md:h-16`, `bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-md`.

---

## Compose, don’t restyle

- Use CVA **variants** (`variant`, `size`) before custom color/typography classes.
- `className` = layout — not recoloring primitives.
- Prefer existing `Button` / `Badge` / `Card` / `Dialog` / `Table` / `Skeleton` / `NoData`.
- Empty → `NoData`; loading → co-located Skeleton ([`SKELETONS.mdc`](SKELETONS.mdc)).

---

## Forbidden (product)

- Raw Tailwind color utilities in product/feature UI
- Marketing aesthetics in dashboard (hero gradients, `text-5xl`, glass, purple blurs)
- `rounded-md` / non-pill on `Button` / `Badge`
- Solid destructive button fills as default
- Custom empty states instead of `NoData`
- Generic muted loaders instead of structured Skeleton
- Inventing new Badge status dialects for domain

---

## Quick checklist

- [ ] Semantic tokens only
- [ ] Radius matches map
- [ ] Control heights `h-8` / button `h-9` or `sm`
- [ ] Icons `size-4` (or documented exception)
- [ ] Empty → `NoData`; loading → Skeleton 1:1
- [ ] Dual `md` layout for data tables
- [ ] Light + dark without hard-coded greys

